OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FQuite cloudy this morning with
OL,6,Fsome rain. Variable amounts of cloud
OL,7,Fand sunny spells in the afternoon
OL,8,Falong with scattered slow moving
OL,9,Fshowers, occasionally heavy and
OL,10,Fthundery. West coast drier later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FScattered heavy showers will
OL,13,Fgradually die out this evening,
OL,14,Fleaving the rest of the night largely
OL,15,Fdry with a few clear spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
