OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA mainly dry, bright
OL,6,Fmorning. Turning overcast through the
OL,7,Fafternoon as a band of occasionally
OL,8,Fheavy rain spreads in from the west.
OL,9,FFreshening afternoon winds,
OL,10,Foccasionally strong in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FBright and breezy on Thursday with
OL,14,Fvariable amounts of cloud and
OL,15,Fscattered showers. Risk of patchy rain
OL,16,Fon Friday and Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
